    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've talked to people. they all just say \"it gets better\" or \"give it time.\" but time is the problem. time is just more silence. more empty rooms. it honestly feels like i'm just delaying the inevitable. why am i even fighting to stay in a world where he doesn't exist? it feels so exhausting to just... exist.",
